{"tid":117553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"首個英文單字車牌「V」拍賣 以天價1300萬元成交","createTime":"2017-02-12T10:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T03:34:42.000Z","uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44481f0e3e1151756fccfa35e10533bfc0675d44","tid":117553,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170212&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56295525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170212%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56295525&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=04ce8af1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170212%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56295525&h=520d130f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170212&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56295525</a><br />\n首個英文單字車牌「V」拍賣 以天價1300萬元成交"},{"pid":"3273f84a05059d44c358bf6d4e31418568e7da80","tid":117553,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"要 聞突 發娛 樂兩 岸更多國 際財 經果 籽體 育馬 經<br />\n首個英文單字車牌「V」拍賣 以天價1300萬元成交<br />\n<br />\n2017-02-12 17:52:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運輸署今日舉行農曆新年車牌拍賣會，推出45個車牌拍賣，其中自訂車牌、單字「V」最為矚目。拍賣官將底價訂為5000元，每口叫價1000元，最終經過逾10次叫價，由一名戴口罩女子以1300萬元投得。運輸署發言人早前指，「V」是首個拍賣的單英文字母車牌。<br />\n<br />\n之前有熟識車牌拍賣的人士估計，成交價或高達500萬元，但最終成交價毫逾千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n上一則: 【短片】【特首選戰】薯片叔籌款逾$500萬 妙論「lesser evil」<br />\n<br />\n下一則: 【短片】【渣馬】跑道上的浪漫！情侶著婚紗跑過第20個馬拉松<br />\n<br />\n桌面版使用說明使用條款聯絡我們<br />\n&copy;2017 AD Internet Limited.<br />\nAll rights reserved. 版權所有 不得轉載"},{"pid":"1a45a887ac3da282532f7fd93a5459fc582f1b1d","tid":117553,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"咁計落去，炒車牌好過炒樓"},{"pid":"7e0e4125b4d6ab377876f999a4d74a03b0311ae9","tid":117553,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁計落去，炒車牌好過炒樓</blockquote><br />\n有千幾萬買車牌，都係炒緊幾億的樓"},{"pid":"bf50b7ec754f2f977a2489079edd7c5ef01cce68","tid":117553,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}